Show HN: BookNotion – Save Kindle highlights to Notion for free
text:
Hi, I'm Sho, a BookNotion developer. I often listen to podcasts, and I often hear my favorite podcasters quoting phrases from books they have read, and I thought to myself, "I wish I could do that too. "

BookNotion is an iOS app that allows you to save the phrases you have highlighted on your Kindle into Notion just by using the Kindle app. We are releasing it in Japan first, and it has been downloaded more than 15,000 times in a few months since its beta release, and users like it very much.

It's free, so give it a try!
